# want to specify a deployment location and name for the log4j log file.

########################## Misc Parameters #################################
# log4j logging level. Must be ALL, TRACE, DEBUG, INFO, WARN, ERROR, FATAL, or
# NONE.  ALL, TRACE, and DEBUG are probably a bad bet for production...
